WEBVTT

00:02:58.430 --> 00:03:02.522
And overnight, because this man
had pulled me in,

00:03:02.546 --> 00:03:07.151
and I had grabbed onto that lifeline
with every fiber of my being,

00:03:07.901 --> 00:03:11.027
I had gone from "Joanie Loves Chachi"

00:03:12.264 --> 00:03:14.258
to full-blown Nazi.

00:03:14.826 --> 00:03:16.004
Overnight.

00:03:17.626 --> 00:03:20.773
I started to listen to the rhetoric

00:03:20.797 --> 00:03:21.952
and believe it.

00:03:22.518 --> 00:03:26.880
I started to watch very closely
as the leaders of this organization

00:03:26.904 --> 00:03:32.059
would target vulnerable young people
who felt marginalized